OL,3,CSir David Beckham to receive Hollywood
OL,4,CWalk of Fame star
OL,6,FFootballer Sir David Beckham will
OL,7,Freceive a star on the Hollywood Walk
OL,8,Fof Fame.
OL,10,FThe Hollywood Chamber of Commerce
OL,11,Fannounced the former England captain
OL,12,Fand Manchester United star will be
OL,13,Fhonoured with a ceremony at 6819
OL,14,FHollywood Boulevard on 12 June.
OL,16,FActor Tom Cruise and Sir David's wife
OL,17,FVictoria will speak at the event, with
OL,18,Fthe 51-year-old receiving the walk's
OL,19,F2,849th star.
