OL,3,CSir David Beckham to receive Hollywood
OL,4,CWalk of Fame star
OL,6,FWalk of Fame producer Ana Martinez
OL,7,Fsaid: "The Hollywood Chamber of
OL,8,FCommerce is proud to welcome David
OL,9,FBeckham to the Hollywood Walk of Fame.
OL,11,F"David Beckham's recognition with a
OL,12,FHollywood Walk of Fame star in the
OL,13,FSports Entertainment category comes at
OL,14,Fa fitting moment as the United States
OL,15,Fprepares to host the Fifa World Cup.
OL,17,F"Beckham's role in elevating soccer's
OL,18,Fprofile in America and his lasting
OL,19,Finfluence on sports, entertainment,
OL,20,Fand global culture make this honour
OL,21,Fespecially meaningful."
OL,26,@oD@GOUsD@AOUyD@AOU}D@WO]
