OL,3,CSir David Beckham to receive Hollywood
OL,4,CWalk of Fame star
OL,6,FThe recognition comes ahead of the
OL,7,F2026 Fifa Men's World Cup, which gets
OL,8,Funder way this month in the US, Mexico
OL,9,Fand Canada.
OL,11,FSir David's playing career spanned 20
OL,12,Fyears and saw him become the first
OL,13,FEnglish player to win league titles in
OL,14,Ffour countries: England, Spain, the
OL,15,FUnited States and France.
OL,17,FIn 2018, he became co-owner of MLS
OL,18,Fclub Inter Miami, which won its first
OL,19,FMLS Cup in 2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
