OL,3,CSir David Beckham to receive Hollywood
OL,4,CWalk of Fame star
OL,6,FAlongside his football career, he has
OL,7,Fsupported a number of charity causes,
OL,8,Fincluding serving as a goodwill
OL,9,Fambassador for humanitarian aid
OL,10,Forganisation Unicef since 2005.
OL,12,FSir David also received a knighthood
OL,13,Fin 2025 for his services to sport and
OL,14,Fcharity.
